nd they bitched to VI.<br><br>And dammit. I actually agree with Veloxia <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :p --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/tongue.gif ALT=":p"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br><br><br><br>Rollen <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/uhocbiena.showPublicProfile?language=EN>HocBiena</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 14<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(6/6/02 2:13:30 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=779.topic&index=10>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Wow..</span><hr size=1> /rant on<br>Well conratulations to myself for being a fool, I got addicted to EQ and will probably keep playing but this really stinks.<br>/bonk<br>/rant off<br><br>I have hoped to see the insides of that zones sometime, maybe in a year or so, now I give up hope to even see the key to enter the place.<br><br>Do I care that it is more difficult on other servers ? NO I play on FV nowhere else. I simply do not care what happens on other servers and what the timelines is for a guild to enter a certain place.<br><br>FV was supposed to be unique, well thanks for taking a motivating factor away.<br><br>/rant on<br>Thankyou for wasting about an hour of my time last night wil the LD on trading, I dont even know what is supposed to be nodrop and what isnt, so suspended trading with anyone till it is fixed.<br><br>BTW vendors also crashed me even when I was selling some stupid pelt. <br>/rant off<br><br>My sympathy to people/guilds who lost keys.<br><br>my 1cp<br>had to get it out of my system. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ueyston.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Eyston</A></span><b